dcpu16 emulator and dissasembler written in c with a Gtk+ UI, glade layout.

To build run scons.
An executable called dcpu will be created in root dir, still depends on src/window.xml

*Command line args not yet finalized*
$dcpu
$dcpu filename.bin
$dcpu filename.bin -d #disassembles


tools/ contains a java app for creating dcpu binary files from plain txt op codes.
